Package ur_rna.RNAstructureUI.menus

A package that holds all menus used in the Java RNAstructure interface.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConstraintsMenu
    A class that creates a folding constraints menu.
    DynamicMenuBar
    A class that creates a menu bar.
    FileMenu
    A class that creates a "File" menu.
    HelpMenu
    A class that creates a "Help" menu.
    NucleicAcidMenu
    A class that creates a menu which holds commands specific for a nucleic acid type.
    RolloverMenu
    A class that creates a menu for the RNAstructure GUI.
